--- input
path = hash:(foo)

--- output
{ "testml": "0.3.0",
  "code": [
    ["=","path",
      [":",
        ["hash"],
        ["foo"]]]],
  "data": []}

=== Variable array index
--- input
path = array:[foo]

--- output
{ "testml": "0.3.0",
  "code": [
    ["=","path",
