=== Point hash index
--- input
*foo:key == 'bar'

--- output
{ "testml": "0.3.0",
  "code": [
    ["%()",["*foo"],
      ["==",
        [":",
          ["*","foo"],
          "key"],
        "bar"]]],
  "data": []}

=== Multiple indices
--- input
x1 = a:'b':3:(d):[e]
--- output
{ "testml": "0.3.0",
  "code": [
    ["=","x1",
      ["[]",
        [":",
          ["[]",
            [":",
              ["a"],
              "b"],
            3],
          ["d"]],
        ["e"]]]],
  "data": []}

